orf-Astoria-Costa-Rica-Punta-Cacique-Arrival.jpg?resize=1536,1152 1536w, https://stories-editor.hilton.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Waldorf-Astoria-Costa-Rica-Punta-Cacique-Arrival.jpg?resize=2048,1536 2048w\" sizes=\"auto, (max-width: 8832px) 100vw, 8832px\" /\u003e\u003cspan aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-cover__background has-black-background-color has-background-dim\"\u003e\u003c/span\u003e\u003cdiv class=\"wp-block-cover__inner-container is-layout-constrained wp-block-cover-is-layout-constrained\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"wp-block-group alignwide is-vertical is-layout-flex wp-container-core-group-is-layout-8cf370e7 wp-block-group-is-layout-flex\"\u003e\n\u003ch2 class=\"wp-block-heading has-white-color has-text-color has-link-color wp-elements-20bf72fbb8ba2fed93345113cbc5c750\"\u003eHilton\u0026#8217;s 2026 Trends Report\u003c/h2\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003ch4 class=\"wp-block-heading is-style-default no-bottom-margin has-white-color has-text-color\"\u003eThe Whycation: Travel\u0026#8217;s New Starting Point\u003c/h4\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv class=\"wp-block-buttons is-layout-flex wp-block-buttons-is-layout-flex\"\u003e\n\u003cdiv class=\"wp-block-button\"\u003e\u003ca class=\"wp-block-button__link has-white-color has-indigo-background-color has-text-color has-background wp-element-button\" href=\"http://stories.hilton.com/2026-trends\"\u003eFull Report\u003c/a\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\n\u003c/div\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\u003cdiv style=\"height:75px\" aria-hidden=\"true\" class=\"wp-block-spacer\"\u003e\u003c/div\u003e\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n\n","protected":false,"blocks":[{"clientId":"0528d0b2-dbf7-42a3-ad0c-a551de9898c5","name":"corpnews-blocks/section","attributes":{"title":"Trending Stories","disableCta":true,"meta":{"has_separator":true,"separator_color":"gradient"},"variation":"trending-stories","cta":{"url":"","text":"See all","opensInNewTab":false},"hasCta":false,"allowedBlock":"corpnews-blocks/posts"},"innerBlocks":[{"clientId":"330782b0-168d-4eb0-b1c5-4f0363028aca","name":"corpnews-blocks/posts","attributes":{"posts":[{"id":42163,"title":{"rendered":"Hilton Introduces the Hilton AI Planner, Advancing the Future of Curated Travel Discovery"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"McLEAN, Va.\u0026nbsp;– Hilton today announced its new\u0026nbsp;Hilton AI Planner, a generative AI–powered digital concierge\u0026nbsp;that\u0026nbsp;helps\u0026nbsp;travelers explore the company’s global portfolio of hotels and plan memorable stays with Hilton. The introduction of the\u0026nbsp;Hilton AI Planner, now in beta testing at hilton.com,\u0026nbsp;addresses the\u0026nbsp;growing use of AI tools for travel planning and\u0026nbsp;underscores Hilton’s long-standing commitment to innovation and investment […]"},"type":"story","date":"2026-03-10T09:15:00","date_gmt":"2026-03-10T13:15:00","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/releases/hilton-introduces-the-hilton-ai-planner","featured_media":42186,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":70},{"id":42188,"title":{"rendered":"Hilton Announces Plans for First Curio Collection by Hilton Hotel in Hawai‘i; Appoints General Manager Ahead of Planned Fall 2026 Opening"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"KAUAʻI, Hawaii and MCLEAN, Va. – Today, Hilton (NYSE: HLT), a global hospitality leader, announced plans for Hale Hōkūala Kauaʻi, Curio Collection by Hilton, marking the lifestyle brand’s first hotel in Hawai‘i, expected to open in fall 2026. Nestled within the Hōkūala Resort community on the island of Kauaʻi, the 210-room new-build hotel is owned […]"},"type":"story","date":"2026-03-10T09:00:00","date_gmt":"2026-03-10T13:00:00","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/releases/hilton-announces-plans-for-first-curio-collection-by-hilton-hotel-in-hawaii","featured_media":42191,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":79},{"id":37354,"title":{"rendered":"Waldorf Astoria Los Cabos Pedregal Completes Final Phase of Multi-Year Property-Wide Transformation"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Originally published: Sept. 25, 2025Updated: March 10, 2026 LOS CABOS, MX –\u0026nbsp;The final phase of Waldorf Astoria Los Cabos Pedregal’s multi-year property-wide transformation is officially complete. The extensive renovation showcases the hotel’s commitment to delivering redefined accommodations and on-property experiences to both new guests and those who have called Waldorf Astoria Los Cabos Pedregal “home” […]"},"type":"story","date":"2025-09-25T14:49:20","date_gmt":"2025-09-25T18:49:20","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/releases/waldorf-astoria-los-cabos-pedregal-debuts-final-phase-of-multi-year-property-wide-transformation","featured_media":42245,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":72},{"id":42201,"title":{"rendered":"Get Front-Row Seats on the Thames: Experience The Boat Race Like a VIP with Hilton Honors"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Every spring, London’s River Thames becomes the stage for the legendary Boat Race between the University of Oxford and the University of Cambridge. It’s one of the most storied rivalries in sport, and millions tune in each year to watch as centuries of tradition, pride, and passion come to life during a row down a […]"},"type":"story","date":"2026-03-09T16:35:36","date_gmt":"2026-03-09T20:35:36","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/destination-spotlight/experience-the-boat-race-like-a-vip-with-hilton-honors","featured_media":42202,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":62}],"maxNumberOfPosts":4,"variation":"trending-stories","postType":["post","story"],"curationType":"manual","taxonomy":"story_category","terms":{"62":{"id":62,"name":"Destination Spotlight","slug":"destination-spotlight","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/category/destination-spotlight","parent":0,"taxonomy":"story_category"},"70":{"id":70,"name":"Innovation","slug":"innovation","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/category/innovation","parent":0,"taxonomy":"story_category"},"72":{"id":72,"name":"Property News","slug":"property-news","link":"https://stories.hilto