w York Unveils Guerlain Wellness Spa, a New Era of Bespoke Wellness"}],"maxNumberOfPosts":7,"loadAsync":true,"postType":["post","story"],"curationType":"manual","taxonomy":"story_category","terms":[],"multipleTerms":true,"queryArgs":[],"numberOfPosts":6,"variation":"","blockContext":[],"meta":[]},"innerBlocks":[]}]}]},{"clientId":"42ce2c8d-59dd-4eea-b9fd-850cdb00b90c","name":"core/cover","attributes":{"url":"https://stories-editor.hilton.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/09/Waldorf-Astoria-Costa-Rica-Punta-Cacique-Arrival.jpg?w=1024","id":37519,"alt":"Waldorf Astoria Costa Rica Punta Cacique. man standing next to staircase overlooking the water and seating area","dimRatio":50,"overlayColor":"black","isUserOverlayColor":true,"focalPoint":{"x":0.5,"y":0.75},"minHeight":450,"contentPosition":"bottom left","sizeSlug":"large","align":"full","className":"no-top-bottom-margin","layout":{"type":"constrained"},"useFeaturedImage":false,"hasParallax":false,"isRepeated":false,"backgroundType":"image","isDark":true,"tagName":"div"},"innerBlocks":[{"clientId":"059d1be9-c785-4b07-90be-e885cefe0999","name":"core/group","attributes":{"align":"wide","layout":{"type":"flex","orientation":"vertical"},"tagName":"div"},"innerBlocks":[{"clientId":"d64310f6-c354-470e-be65-52f54bf16a2b","name":"core/heading","attributes":{"style":{"elements":{"link":{"color":{"text":"var:preset|color|white"}}}},"textColor":"white","content":"Hilton's 2026 Trends Report","level":2},"innerBlocks":[]},{"clientId":"cf6c0788-19bc-435d-802c-b8c1651d8cf7","name":"core/heading","attributes":{"level":4,"className":"is-style-default no-bottom-margin","textColor":"white","content":"The Whycation: Travel's New Starting Point"},"innerBlocks":[]},{"clientId":"f797731b-c54e-4047-8d62-f7a6182807e6","name":"core/buttons","attributes":[],"innerBlocks":[{"clientId":"bfadb48f-cf6b-4100-8036-3b7f1204f7f2","name":"core/button","attributes":{"tagName":"a","type":"button","url":"http://stories.hilton.com/2026-trends","text":"Full Report"},"innerBlocks":[]}]}]}]},{"clientId":"2ceef71d-5a16-4f9a-8865-1bafa1497aad","name":"core/spacer","attributes":{"height":"75px"},"innerBlocks":[]},{"clientId":"0c2dbbb6-ec38-4f33-98ad-7804ef60a262","name":"corpnews-blocks/section","attributes":{"title":"Latest Openings","cta":{"url":"/category/latest-openings","text":"See All Openings","opensInNewTab":false},"hasCta":true,"meta":{"has_separator":true,"separator_color":"magenta"},"variation":"stories-carousel","disableCta":false,"allowedBlock":"corpnews-blocks/posts"},"innerBlocks":[{"clientId":"91e64f27-8a74-4490-a285-a422b057c630","name":"corpnews-blocks/posts","attributes":{"curationType":"automatic","terms":{"68":{"id":68,"name":"Latest Openings","slug":"latest-openings","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/category/latest-openings","parent":0,"taxonomy":"story_category"},"110":{"id":110,"name":"Growth \u0026amp; Development","slug":"growth-development","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/category/growth-development","parent":0,"taxonomy":"story_category"}},"numberOfPosts":10,"variation":"stories-carousel","posts":[{"id":42122,"title":{"rendered":"The Highly Awaited Monarch San Antonio Opens Its Doors, Ushering in a New Era for Downtown"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"SAN ANTONIO — More than a decade in the making, one of Texas’s most anticipated hotels makes its long-awaited debut as The Monarch San Antonio, Curio Collection by Hilton opens today in the reimagined Hemisfair District, marking a defining new chapter for the city’s hotel landscape with stays now available. Rising 17 stories at the […]"},"type":"story","date":"2026-03-03T13:11:16","date_gmt":"2026-03-03T18:11:16","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/releases/the-highly-awaited-monarch-san-antonio-now-open","featured_media":42131,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":68},{"id":41401,"title":{"rendered":"India’s Largest DoubleTree by Hilton Opens Near Bengaluru International Airport, Marking Hilton’s Eighth Hotel in the City"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"BENGALURU, India – February 2nd, 2026 – Hilton (NYSE: HLT) today announced the opening of DoubleTree by Hilton Bengaluru Airport, the brand’s largest hotel in India. The opening joins seven Hilton hotels operating in Bengaluru and solidifies Hilton’s multi brand-presence in the city, from luxury, full-service and focused-service offerings. Developed in partnership with Dangayach Group, the hotel brings DoubleTree by […]"},"type":"story","date":"2026-02-02T00:31:00","date_gmt":"2026-02-02T05:31:00","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/releases/indias-largest-doubletree-by-hilton-opens-near-bengaluru-international-airport","featured_media":41402,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":110},{"id":41342,"title":{"rendered":"Hilton Expands its Portfolio in Makkah with the Opening of Two New Hotels"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"RIYADH, Saudi Arabia – Hilton today announced the opening of two new properties in Makkah, nearly doubling its presence in the Holy City and expanding its hospitality offerings for the millions of pilgrims and travelers who visit each year. The openings include DoubleTree by Hilton Makkah Aziziyah, bringing the brand’s signature warm welcome to the […]"},"type":"story","date":"2026-01-28T08:38:58","date_gmt":"2026-01-28T13:38:58","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/releases/hilton-expands-its-portfolio-in-makkah-opening-two-new-hotels","featured_media":41343,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":110},{"id":41270,"title":{"rendered":"Cameo Beverly Hills, LXR Hotels \u0026amp; Resorts Debuts Following Complete Transformation"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"LOS ANGELES, Calif. – Today, Cameo Beverly Hills, LXR Hotels \u0026amp; Resorts emerges as a refined new chapter in Los Angeles luxury, following a complete transformation that reimagines every corner of the property. Tucked along a tranquil edge of Beverly Hills, this hidden oasis provides a peaceful retreat just moments from the lively pulse and […]"},"type":"story","date":"2026-01-26T14:00:00","date_gmt":"2026-01-26T19:00:00","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/releases/cameo-beverly-hills-lxr-hotels-resorts-debuts-following-complete-transformation","featured_media":41260,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":68},{"id":40843,"title":{"rendered":"From Brazil to Morocco, Here’s Where Hilton is Opening and Renovating This Season"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"Hilton is launching a dynamic lineup of new hotels and renovations in early 2026, with brand debuts including Waldorf Astoria in Morocco, Motto by Hilton in Brazil and the first lifestyle hotel in India with the debut of Curio Collection by Hilton in Bengaluru. Spark by Hilton also will debut in the Middle East this […]"},"type":"story","date":"2026-01-22T09:01:14","date_gmt":"2026-01-22T14:01:14","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/growth-development/where-hilton-is-opening-and-renovating-this-season-2026-q1","featured_media":40842,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":110},{"id":41096,"title":{"rendered":"Hotel Heron, An Aparium Group Hotel, Joins Curio Collection by Hilton"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"ALEXANDRIA, Va. \u0026#8211; Hotel Heron, an Aparium hotel known for its thoughtful design and connection to the local community, has announced its transition to Curio Collection by Hilton, a global portfolio of individually remarkable hotels hand-picked to immerse guests in the world’s most sought-after destinations. The 134-room property will retain its distinct character as it continues […]"},"type":"story","date":"2026-01-21T09:48:07","date_gmt":"2026-01-21T14:48:07","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/releases/hotel-heron-an-aparium-group-hotel-joins-curio-collection-by-hilton","featured_media":41122,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":110},{"id":40767,"title":{"rendered":"Hilton Expands Flagship Brand in Bangkok with Opening of Hilton Bangkok Suvarnabhumi Golf Resort \u0026#038; Spa"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"BANGKOK, Thailand –      Hilton (NYSE: HLT) announced the opening of Hilton Bangkok Suvarnabhumi Golf Resort \u0026amp; Spa, strengthening the presence of its flagship brand in Thailand’s capital. The opening marks the hospitality company’s fourth Hilton Hotel \u0026amp; Resorts property in Bangkok, joining Millennium Hilton Bangkok, Hilton Bangkok Grande Asoke, and Hilton Sukhumvit Bangkok.   As […]"},"type":"story","date":"2026-01-14T10:21:14","date_gmt":"2026-01-14T15:21:14","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/releases/hilton-expands-flagship-brand-in-bangkok-with-opening-of-hilton-bangkok-suvarnabhumi-golf-resort-spa","featured_media":40768,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":110},{"id":40736,"title":{"rendered":"Zaria Court Kigali Now Open as Part of Tapestry Collection by Hilton"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"KIGALI, Rwanda – Zaria Court Kigali is now officially open as part of Tapestry Collection by Hilton, marking a transformative milestone for Rwanda\u0026#8217;s first urban lifestyle hotel and reinforcing the nation\u0026#8217;s expanding presence in the global hospitality landscape. This new chapter brings together Zaria Court Kigali’s distinctive identity, rooted in authentic African excellence and vibrant […]"},"type":"story","date":"2026-01-13T10:52:12","date_gmt":"2026-01-13T15:52:12","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/releases/zaria-court-kigali-now-open-as-part-of-tapestry-collection-by-hilton","featured_media":40737,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":110},{"id":40629,"title":{"rendered":"Motto by Hilton Opens in Downtown Nashville"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"NASHVILLE, Tenn. \u0026#8211; Motto by Hilton Nashville Downtown opened this month in Music City, bringing connected, community-driven stays to the South of Broadway (SoBro) neighborhood. Managed by Chartwell Hospitality and owned by Apple Hospitality REIT, Inc., the 13-story, 260-room hotel offers guests cleverly compact rooms with more flexibility than ever, serving as the perfect launchpad […]"},"type":"story","date":"2026-01-13T09:47:10","date_gmt":"2026-01-13T14:47:10","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/releases/motto-by-hilton-opens-in-downtown-nashville","featured_media":40634,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":68},{"id":40496,"title":{"rendered":"A New Chapter for Barr Al Jissah: Hilton Opens Three Hotels on Oman’s Iconic Coastline"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"MUSCAT, Oman – Hilton (NYSE: HLT) has introduced three hotels at Barr Al Jissah, a landmark waterfront destination celebrated for its natural beauty. Nestled between the cliffs of Al Jissah and the Gulf of Oman, the properties offer a blend of family-friendly options, vibrant event spaces, and elevated luxury experiences. Owned by The Zubair Corporation […]"},"type":"story","date":"2026-01-05T09:58:51","date_gmt":"2026-01-05T14:58:51","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/releases/hilton-opens-three-hotels-on-omans-iconic-coastline-barr-al-jissah","featured_media":40497,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":110}],"postType":["post","story"],"taxonomy":"story_category","multipleTerms":true,"queryArgs":[],"maxNumberOfPosts":0,"blockContext":[],"loadAsync":false,"meta":[],"images":{"40497":{"alt_text":"An aerial shot of the hotel next to the ocean","media_details":{"sizes":{"full":{"source_url":"https://stories-editor.hilton.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Al-Husn-Hotel-Muscat.jpg","width":8064,"height":4536}},"width":8064,"height":4536},"source_url":"https://stories-editor.hilton.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Al-Husn-Hotel-Muscat.jpg"},"40634":{"alt_text":"Motto by Hilton Nashville Downtown Guest Room with bed an end table next to a window and mounted television","media_details":{"sizes":{"full":{"source_url":"https://stories-editor.hilton.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Motto-by-Hilton-Nashville-Downtown-Guest-Room-Kirsten-Holliday-Photography.jpg","width":1024,"height":682}},"width":1024,"height":682},"source_url":"https://stories-editor.hilton.com/wp-content/uploads/2026/01/Motto-by-Hilton-Nashville-Downtown-Guest-Room-Kirsten-Holliday-Photography.jpg"},"40737"