: Hilton Honors Introduces Faster Path to Elite Status and Reveals New Premium Tier – Diamond Reserve"},"excerpt":{"rendered":"MCLEAN, Va.\u0026nbsp;– Committed to rewarding loyalty at every stage of the travel journey, today Hilton (NYSE: HLT) announced\u0026nbsp;exciting\u0026nbsp;changes\u0026nbsp;to\u0026nbsp;its award-winning Hilton Honors loyalty program. Debuting this January, Hilton will introduce its most elite tier yet \u0026#8211; Diamond Reserve – with new elevated benefits, including a Confirmable Upgrade Reward that can be instantly redeemed at the time\u0026nbsp;of\u0026nbsp;booking, […]"},"type":"story","date":"2025-11-18T07:00:10","date_gmt":"2025-11-18T12:00:10","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/releases/loyalty-upgraded-hilton-honors-introduces-faster-path-to-elite-status-and-reveals-new-premium-tier-diamond-reserve","featured_media":39458,"meta":[],"is_external":false,"primary_term":65}],"maxNumberOfPosts":2,"variation":"two-columns-grid","postType":["post","story"],"curationType":"manual","taxonomy":"story_category","terms":{"65":{"id":65,"name":"Hilton Honors","slug":"hilton-honors","link":"https://stories.hilton.com/category/hilton-honors","parent":0,"taxonomy":"story_category"}},"multipleTerms":true,"queryArgs":[],"numberOfPosts":6,"blockContext":[],"loadAsync":false,"meta":[],"images":{"39458":{"alt_text":"Waldorf Astoria New York - Lex Yard, People sitting on green upholstered barstools and leather chairs in a bar drinking cocktails in coup glassed with a bartender pouring a drink, American brasserie, casually elegant dining room and lively bar, green bar stools","media_details":{"sizes":{"full":{"source_url":"https://stories-editor.hilton.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Waldorf-Astoria-New-York_Lex-Yard.jpg","width":8256,"height":5504}},"width":8256,"height":5504},"source_url":"https://stories-editor.hilton.com/wp-content/uploads/2025/11/Waldorf-Astoria-New-York_Lex-Yard.jpg"},"40008":{"alt_text":"Explora Journeys - EXPLORA I - New York","